entropy.configuration.graphics

Class Disposition

  • java.lang.Object
    • entropy.configuration.graphics.Disposition

  • public class Disposition
extends Object
    a disposition places an Element, its target.
    The target touches a left and top positions, or null. They are the lAnchor and tAnchor.
    Author:
    guillaume
